        h2(style="font-size: 40px") Meet Henry Soong! 
      p(style="font-size:20px; line-height: 150%;")
        | After college, I decided to venture away from my native Chicago and taught math at a high school in Oakland as part of the Teach for America program. After TFA, I worked on a machine learning project with an agricultural robotics startup in Mountain View. PMs at Facebook come from a variety of disciplines, places, and world views. My favorite part of being an RPM is getting to see people think out loud during brainstorm sessions. There is such creativity and passion! Fun fact: I'm a die hard Planet Earth fan! Shark week has nothing on their super slo-mo Great White Shark scenes. 
